# Terraform
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfstate.backup
*.tfplan
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# Helm
*.tgz
charts/
Chart.lock

# Kubernetes secrets — never commit raw secrets
**/secrets/*.yaml
!**/secrets/README.md
**/sealed-secrets/raw/

# ArgoCD
argocd-initial-admin-secret.txt

# Environment files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

# Shell history
.bash_history
.zsh_history

# Python (used in scripts)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/

# Logs
*.log
logs/
/tmp/

# Generated docs (regenerate with make docs)
terraform/eks/README.md
terraform/gke/README.md
terraform/aks/README.md

# Local override files for personal config
*.local.tfvars
terraform/environments/production.tfvars
terraform/environments/staging.tfvars
!terraform/environments/example.tfvars
